Comments to say when this is used. Final?

Code like this makes me wish for greater use of namespaces. Having something called art::MemoryAllocator could clearly have a meaning in the runtime. The runtime's allocators are buried in art::gc:allocator::... so as a random person you may well come across this code first and think its to do with the garbage collector.

